description.en:
**Volume 1 (2018)**
Cover: Kawai Makoto
Chapters:
1. Chikakute Tooi (近くて遠い) [2C=Galore]
2. Yasetai-san to Shitsuren-chan (痩せたいさんと失恋ちゃん) [Writer: Yasuda Kousuke, Artist: Fumio Aya]
3. Dokuryou Made Ato Dono Kurai (読了まであとどのくらい) [Taiboku]
4. Watashi no Sukina Shoutengai (私の好きな商店街) [Mirai Denki]
5. Kanibaruru Ichi Mushi Shea (かにばるる一むしぇあ) [Goumoto]
6. Boukun Platonic (暴君プラトニック) [Kinoue Seiichi]
7. Onii-chan no Kanojo (お兄ちゃんの彼女) [Omi Kohara]
8. Taiju no Miyako (大樹の都) [Biyora]
9. Kinyou no Yoru wa (金曜の夜は) [Saki Hajime]
10. Miori to Yamagami-sama (未織と山神様) [Tokomichi]
11. Yari-sugi Skinship (やりすぎスキンシップ) [Akitsuki Itsuki]
12. Futari Wake (ふたりわけ) [Otaki]
13. Tane Lab manga do it (たねラボ manga do it) [Hayashiya Shizuru]

**Volume 2 (2019)**
Cover: Kawai Makoto
Chapters:

14. Tomodachi no Tomodachi wa Tomodachi janai (友達の友達は友達じゃない) [Utatane Yuu]
15. Nishi-san to Azuma-san (西さんと東さん) [U-temo]
16. Tsubaki Kawai ya (椿かわいや) [Marukawa]
17. Aoi no Yuki Usagi (あおいのゆきうさぎ) [Tokomichi]
18. Italian Beef (イタリアンビーフ) [Writer: Aoki Juntarou, Artist: Shina Yoshinao]
19. FRIDAY IS THE DAY [Hayashiya Shizuru]
20. Jingi Naki Otometachi (仁義なき百合たち) [Indo Curry]
21. YOU wa Real no Vtuber (YOUはリアルのVtuber) [Utsurogi Angu]
22. Futari no Kizu-mei (二人の傷名) [Shikio Satoru]
23. Mangaka-chan to Henshuu-san (まんが家ちゃんと編集さん) [Marin]
24. Marumaru Shikaji ka (まるまるしかじか) [Fukumaaya]
25. Gyaru desu ga, Kurasu no Jimiko ni Kyuukon Sareteimasu (ギャルですが、クラスの地味子に求婚されています) [Yukio Yuki]
26. Shimaigurashi (しまいぐらし) [Otaki]
27. Tsuno wo Tamete Jibun wo Korosu (角を矯めて自分を殺す) [Dowman Sayman]
28. Blue • Miserable no Shiro (ブルー•ミゼラブルの城) [Chino Machico]

**Volume 3 (2020)**
Cover: Kawai Makoto
Chapters:

29. Chidjinde Nobiru (ちぢんでのびる) [Fujichika Koume]
30. Darashinai Onna (だらしない女) [Miura Kozumi]
31. OVERWRITE LILY [Fukamizu Tiroli]
32. Atara yo no Futari (あたらよのふたり) [Dr. pepperco]
33. Isso Fumi Tsubushite (いっそ踏み潰して) [Okapaya]
34. Tanaka Encounter! (田中エンカウント！) [Kaneko Aru]
35. HONEY,DARLIN’ [Toono Inunohi]
36. Tomodachi Iinkai (トモダチ委員会) [Otaki]
37. Futatsu no Yama no Mukougawa (ふたつの山の向こう側) [Yuu]
38. Natsukage (夏陰) [Amazaki Suika]
39. Doppel Anata(ドッペルあなた) [Tsutsui]
40. Imawa no Sai no Kokuhaku (いまわの際の告白) [Niina Ryou]
41. Amai Kanojo (あまいかのじょ) [Fujisaki Yuu]
42. Amber Honey (アンバーハニー) [Ohkita Mahiro]
43. Nami dame no Kingyo (なみだめの金魚) [Emoto Haru]

**Alt names**:

**Name In Native Language:** 道満晴明 (Douman Seiman)

**Also Known As:** 飯島進 (Iijima Susumu)

**Birth:** March 7
**Years active:** 1993-Present
**Hometown:** Chiba, Japan

**Circle:** 
G Kun Dow (ジークンドー)
Kiheitai (畸兵隊)

His current art style was directly influenced by Mike Mignola (Dowman is a fan of Hellboy).

An avid fan of horror movies (the witches in Voynich Hotel were named after an obscure Italian horror trilogy). After graduating from a design vocational school, he made his debut in the publishing section of BANDAI drawing manga for videogame anthologies.

His pen name is based on the two legendary onmyouji, Abe no Seimei and Ashiya Doman.

**Name In Native Language:** 結布

**Also Known As:** mol
